article.headline: Leach scores 20 as Fairfield beats Fairleigh Dickinson 92-69
article.description: — Jalen Leach's 20 points helped Fairfield defeat Fairleigh Dickinson 92-69 on Thursday night.
article.linkText: Leach scores 20 as Fairfield beats Fairleigh Dickinson 92-69
article.story: TEANECK, N.J. -- — Jalen Leach's 20 points helped Fairfield defeat Fairleigh Dickinson 92-69 on Thursday night. Leach added eight rebounds for the Stags (6-6). Caleb Fields scored 17 points, shooting 5 for 9, including 5 for 7 from beyond the arc. Birima Seck finished 6 of 7 from the floor to finish with 13 points. Jo'el Emanuel led the way for the Knights (6-7) with 18 points. Ansley Almonor added 15 points and nine rebounds for Fairleigh Dickinson. In addition, DeVante Jamison had eight points. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
